es, souvenirs, or a more relaxed pace.  \\n\\nEnjoy the sun, sea, and spice of Goa! \ud83c\udf1e\ud83c\udfd6\ufe0f\ud83c\udf64\",\"type\":\"TextMessage\"}}", "sender": "Travel_Planner_d2c25980-0073-4990-a29b-52f7c7abf9fc/d2c25980-0073-4990-a29b-52f7c7abf9fc", "receiver": null, "kind": "MessageKind.PUBLISH", "delivery_stage": "DeliveryStage.DELIVER", "type": "Message"}
