20b9300** |\\n| Optional Breakfast (2\u202fdays \u00d7\u202f\u20b9250) | **\u20b9500** |\\n| Airport transfer (private car, round\u2011trip) | **\u20b91\u202f400** |\\n| **Total Approx.** | **\u20b97\u202f000\u202f\u2013\u202f\u20b97\u202f500** (\u2248\u202f$90\u2011$95) |\\n\\nEven with a modest addition for meals and transport, you stay well under a **\u20b910\u202f000** budget for accommodation and basic logistics, leaving plenty of room for food, activities, and souvenirs within a typical **\u20b930\u202f000\u2011\u20b940\u202f000** 2\u2011day Goa trip budget.\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Want a Quick Booking Link?\\n\\n- **Agoda \u2013 Superior Room (\u20b92\u202f212/night)**: https://www.agoda.com/the-flora-residency/calangute-india/hotel/xxxx  \\n- **Booking.com \u2013 Superior Room (Free Cancel)**: https://www.booking.com/hotel/in/the-flora-residency/calangute.html  \\n\\n*(Replace \u201cxxxx\u201d with the actual hotel ID; the link will auto\u2011populate the current rate.)*\\n\\nFeel free to ask if you need help arranging airport transfers, day\u2011trip itineraries, or any other travel details! \ud83c\udf34\u2708\ufe0f\ud83c\udfe8\",\"type\":\"TextMessage\"}}", "sender": "Travel_Planner_d2c25980-0073-4990-a29b-52f7c7abf9fc/d2c25980-0073-4990-a29b-52f7c7abf9fc", "receiver": "output_topic_d2c25980-0073-4990-a29b-52f7c7abf9fc/d2c25980-0073-4990-a29b-52f7c7abf9fc", "kind": "MessageKind.PUBLISH", "delivery_stage": "DeliveryStage.SEND", "type": "Message"}
